The Radiant Minimalist Bridal Look✨

A clean girl-inspired Indian bridal makeover that blends glow with grace. Skin is fresh and dewy, with a soft-focus base that looks lit-from-within. Eyes shimmer subtly with nude-gold tones, paired with natural lashes and softly defined brows. 

A peachy blush, glossy lips, and a touch of highlighter complete the effortlessly elegant, modern bridal vibe!
